<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pokémon Starters</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f0f0; margin: 0; }
        .navbar { background-color: #CC0000; overflow: hidden; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
        .navbar a { color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; }
        .navbar a:hover { background-color: #3B4CCA; }
        
        /* Flexbox Layout for Starters */
        .starter-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid #3B4CCA;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .card img { width: 200px; height: 200px; } /* Specific sizes */
        h1 { text-align: center; color: #CC0000; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="WrapUpHome.html">Home</a>
        <a href="WrapUp2.html">Starters</a>
        <a href="WrapUp3.html">Battle Basics</a>
        <a href="reference.html">References</a>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h1>Choose Your Partner</h1>
        <div class="starter-container">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Bulbasaur</h3>
                <img src="https://assets.pokemon.com/assets/cms2/img/pokedex/full/001.png" alt="Bulbasaur">
                <p>A Grass-type Pokémon that is very loyal to its trainer.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Charmander</h3>
                <img src="https://assets.pokemon.com/assets/cms2/img/pokedex/full/004.png" alt="Charmander">
                <p>A Fire-type Pokémon with a flame on its tail that shows its mood.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Squirtle</h3>
                <img src="https://assets.pokemon.com/assets/cms2/img/pokedex/full/007.png" alt="Squirtle">
                <p>A Water-type Pokémon known for its powerful shell and water jets.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <p>Choosing a starter is the most important decision in your journey. 
            Each choice changes your strategy for the first few gyms. 
            Bulbasaur is great for beginners because it has an advantage against 
            the first two gym leaders, Brock and Misty. Charmander is a challenge 
            early on but becomes the powerful Charizard later. Squirtle offers a 
            balanced middle ground with high defense. Make sure to think carefully 
            about which elemental type fits your personality and your desired 
            playstyle as you explore the vast Kanto region and beyond!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
